#what you need is : 
ubuntu 14.04,sogou pinyin deb which download from the intnet,add fcitx framwork.
steps
1.download sogou pinyin input method.
2.im-config choose fcitx
3.restart you computer.
4.input fcitx-config-gtk3  in terminal.
5.unslected only show current Language.
6.modify the default im
7.done
